Name: Doll of Resurrection
About the game: 'This game represents the abandonment of objects against the arrogance of human beings.' She/it can be inflated to stand up, inflated to float, or deflate air through narrow gaps. Little heart pricks your skin and flames. Because it will explode her/it. Collect as many stars as possible during the game. It's a very difficult game. Because in reality, an inflatable doll can be very difficult to resist. So we tried to simulate real life as much as possible. Let you experience what it's like to be a sex doll.
